s/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f0fe3f4acd4c5545561796a4efa4f1394079ec8","tid":54003,"uid":29863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T08:40:08.000Z","msg":"推出到先算"},{"pid":"9d7aaad8595e4e3691967d489fefe50c8a0add83","tid":54003,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T08:42:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>石油佬出動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n被失蹤</blockquote><br />\n好快就會有幾百份科研報告發佈話技術唔可行，再恐嚇所有開發者同投資者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2608a542395bbd49e06b35f15a30b377f9ca4ff","tid":54003,"uid":2403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T09:22:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日聽到呢D野<br />\n但有幾多係真係成事?<br />\n以前夠話唔知乜野香港少女整到電池 最後咪又係無左聲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c684f3e060ed4062d0d5710fb4bffee5af50c0e","tid":54003,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T09:24:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日聽到呢D野<br />\n但有幾多係真係成事?<br />\n以前夠話唔知乜野香港少女整到電池 最後咪又係無左聲</blockquote><br />\n無法量產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f526af793e4d8343e94d8b7a146a5b56ba8d42f","tid":54003,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T09:42:28.000Z","msg":"HK01 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nRepost <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nOld news <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46852c5e5691a3dabeabb9da71da9b444680f266","tid":54003,"uid":33528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T09:51:12.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"82b09e589514ffb03f70662e81e3ff17edbe320e","tid":54003,"uid":59746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T09:55:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日聽到呢D野<br />\n但有幾多係真係成事?<br />\n以前夠話唔知乜野香港少女整到電池 最後咪又係無左聲</blockquote><br />\n其實一路都發展緊"},{"pid":"c13af8b8f4a8f11dbdfa658c0a6dc1086a08e03d","tid":54003,"uid":35995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T09:58:25.000Z","msg":"假的都是夢"},{"pid":"720cc54a7cc689e97685e57e43f594f927ceb241","tid":54003,"uid":37090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T10:18:00.000Z","msg":"title點解要用半顆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b4414be9d0cd4fde193747397b6de8b7194a50","tid":54003,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T10:24:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}